<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="hardly-when">hardly … when</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>刚…就：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The girl had hardly rung the bell before the door was opened suddenly.
女孩刚要按门铃，门突然开了。</p><footer>2010 福建</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Hardly had Mike picked up the ball when another player took it from him. 
麦克刚接到球，另一名球员就把球抢走了。</p><footer> 外研⑦ – 7</footer></div>

<p>注: hardly ... when结构中，由when引导的从句用过去时，主句用过去完成时；hardly置于句首时句子要倒装，通常用于非常正式的书面语中。  </p></div>